[{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0018","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-7269","title":"UC Gateway Investment SiteEngine 5.0 URL 重定向漏洞","description":"SiteEngine 5.x 的 api.php 文件存在开放重定向漏洞，攻击者通过在 logout 动作的 forward 参数中构造恶意 URL，诱导已登录用户点击后将其重定向至任意外部网站，进而实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞源于程序对用户输入的 forward 参数未进行充分校验，属于输入验证不完善（CWE-20）导致的安全问题。CVSS 评分为 5.8，危害等级中危，攻击复杂度较低，但需要用户交互配合才能完成利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2008-7269"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-01T16:06:12.770","updated":"2026-06-16T23:03:57.420","remediation":"升级 SiteEngine 至最新版本，或手动修复 api.php 文件：对 `forward` 参数进行白名单校验，仅允许跳转至本站域名内的 URL；拒绝外部域名重定向请求。如无法修改代码，可在 Web 服务器（Nginx/Apache）层面添加规则拦截包含 `forward=http` 或 `forward=//` 的请求参数作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497747/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31888","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6823","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/32523","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-7269.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-7269.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-7269.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/2008/7xxx/CVE-2008-7269.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-7269_2.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d64fd6053930ee34fd56cc0cd403ec7e8d566761/CVE/data/2008/CVE-2008-7269.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2008/CVE-2008-7269.json","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2008/CVE-2008-7269.rules","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-7269_36.yaml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/aadd8a04d5c1c0ece3c9cadfc91f45d3ae7c56c6/CVE-2008/CVE-2008-72xx/CVE-2008-7269.json","https://github.com/2099383411/yunjing/blob/12afcd571c86ce3de52fb7b65e3b538b444e4666/data/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-7269.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0017","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-6982","title":"devalcms 1.4a 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"devalcms 1.4a 的 index.php 文件中存在反射型跨站脚本漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 currentpath 参数注入恶意 HTML 或 JavaScript 代码触发该漏洞，当管理员或用户访问特制链接时，恶意脚本将在受害者浏览器中执行，导致敏感信息泄露（如 Cookie 窃取、会话劫持）或页面内容篡改。该漏洞无需认证即可利用，攻击复杂度较高。目前官方已停止维护，建议迁移至其他 CMS 系统。CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2008-6982"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-08-19T05:24:52.360","updated":"2026-06-16T23:03:21.723","remediation":"升级 devalcms 至 1.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 currentpath 参数未正确过滤转义导致的 XSS 问题。若厂商已停止维护，建议在 index.php 中对 currentpath 参数执行 htmlspecialchars 或 strip_tags 过滤，同时部署 WAF 规则拦截包含恶意脚本的请求作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/47971","http://sourceforge.net/projects/devalcms/files/devalcms/devalcms-1.4b/devalcms-1.4b.zip/download","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31037","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/44940","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6369","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6982.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-6982.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6982.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/20