"2009-03-13T10:30:00.577","updated":"2026-06-16T23:02:16.683","remediation":"升级 Parallels H-Sphere 至 3.1 P1 之后的修复版本（如 3.1 P2 或更高），该版本已对 login.php 中 err、errorcode、login 参数做输出编码处理。若产品已停止维护无法升级，建议在 Web 服务器层（如 Apache mod_security）编写规则过滤含 <script> 等标签的请求参数，并对 login.php 的上述参数实施严格的输入验证和 HTML 实体编码输出，防止恶意脚本注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/48232","http://secunia.com/advisories/31830","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31256","http://www.xssing.com/index.php?x=3&y=65","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/45252","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/45254","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6465.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-6465.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6465.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/2008/6xxx/CVE-2008-6465.json","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2008/README.md","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/CVE-2008-6465.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/30c082f6aec54c3623618927fd86afa06ffe0d2b/api/2008/CVE-2008-6465.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-6465_34.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-6465_2.yaml","https://github.com/damn77789/nuclei-pocs/blob/81fb60243f8c8e930e9c4f1b65e2110e6e5a9204/folder-1/CVE-2008-6465.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/4f5d48b1c3a330d141e8b88dc72924e575aa6154/2008/CVE-2008-6465.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0014","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-6222","title":"Joomla! Pro Desk Support Center 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Pro Desk Support Center (com_pro_desk) 组件 1.0 及 1.2 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 include_file 参数传递包含 `..` 序列的恶意路径，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛低。建议升级至官方修复版本或移除受影响组件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2008-6222"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-02-20T21:30:01.517","updated":"2026-06-16T23:01:50.537","remediation":"立即卸载 Pro Desk Support Center (com_pro_desk) 组件 1.0/1.2 版本，该组件已停止维护，无安全更新可用。若业务依赖，请升级至已修复目录遍历漏洞的 ProDesk 1.5 及以上版本，并在服务端配置禁用 `include_file` 参数的路径回溯（`../`）输入。同时启用 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）规则，拦截路径遍历关键词如 `..%2f` 和 `../../`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/32523","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/32113","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/46356","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6980","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15460","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6222.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-6222.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6222.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/2008/6xxx/CVE-2008-6222.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2008-6222-1394.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2008-6222-1393.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-6222_15.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2008/CVE-2008-6222","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2008-6222-1392.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Sep/26/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/nuclei/nuclei.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0013","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-6172","title":"Weberr RWCards Joomla! 组件路径遍历漏洞","description":"Weberr 公司开发的 Joomla! 组件 RWCards 3.0.11 版本中 captcha/captcha_image.php 存在目录遍历漏洞。当 PHP 配置选项 magic_quotes_gpc 被禁用时，远程攻击者可通过 img 参数构造特制的目录遍历序列（如 ../），实现包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞可导致敏感信息泄露或进一步获取服务器控制权限，影响运行该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2008-6172"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-02-19T16:30:00.407","updated":"2026-06-16T23:01:45.123","remediation":"建议立即卸载 RWCards 3.0.11 组件（该组件已停止维护），更换为仍在活跃开发的 Joomla! 卡片类扩展。如无法卸载，可手动编辑 captcha/captcha_image.php，对 img 参数使用 realpath() 解析并校验路径是否在预期目录内，同时过滤所有包含 ../ 的目录跳转序列。此外，在 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteRule 阻止对 captcha/ 目录的直接恶意请求。PHP 配置中禁用 allow_url_fopen 和 allow_url_include 可降低本地文件包含带来的后续风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/32367","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31892","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/46081","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6817","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6172.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-6172.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6172.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/2008/6xxx/CVE-2008-6172.json","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2008-6172.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2008-6172-1391.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2008-6172.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2008-6172-1388.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/z-11753.yaml","https://github.com/runZeroInc/nuclei-templates/blob/89af8e391d368228625addfe3ecc6aee3b5d0345/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6172.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Mar/12/Reports/Report.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0012","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-6080","title":"Joomla! ionFiles 4.4.2 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 ionFiles 组件（com_ionfiles）4.4.2 版本中的 download.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 file 参数中插入 `..` 序列实现路径跳转，进而读取服务器上任意敏感文件，如配置文件、数据库凭证等。该漏洞源于对用户输入的 file 参数缺乏充分的路径过滤与安全检查，影响范围涉及所有使用该版本组件的 Joomla! 网站，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2008-6080"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-02-06T11:30:00.377","updated":"2026-06-16T23:01:33.777","remediation":"The user wants me to generate a [remediation] field for CVE-2008-6080. This is an old Joomla component vulnerability - a directory traversal in ionFiles 4.4.2 component for Joomla!. Let me think about what remediation makes sense here.\n\nSince this is a very old CVE (2008) for a Joomla component (com_ionfiles 4.4.2), the realistic remediation would be:\n1. Upgrade to a patched version of the component (if available)\n2. Remove/uninstall the vulnerable component if no patch exists\n3. Configure the web server to block directory traversal attempts\n4. As a mitigation, restrict access to the component\n\nSince this is a third-party Joomla component from 2008 that is likely abandoned, the most practical advice would be to upgrade to the latest version or uninstall it. Let me search for more information first.\n\nActually, let me check if there's any patch information available. The vulnerability is in ionFiles 4.4.2 component. Given it's from 2008, the component is likely discontinued. The most practical remediation would be to remove the component or apply a workaround.\n\nLet me search for more context.The vulnerability is CVE-2008-6080, a directory traversal in the ionFiles 4.4.2 component for Joomla!. This is an old third-party component that is likely discontinued.\n\nThe remediation should be practical and specific. Given:\n1. It's a Joomla component from 2008 - likely abandoned\n2. It's a directory traversal via download.php?file= parameter\n3. The component is com_ionfiles version 4.4.2\n\nThe practical remediation would be:\n1. Remove/uninstall the com_ionfiles component if not needed\n2. If needed, apply input validation to the `file` parameter in download.php to prevent directory traversal\n3. Upgrade to a patched version if available\n4. Use .htaccess to restrict access to the component directory\n\nSince I can't find information about a patched version (the component is likely abandoned given it's from 2008), the most practical advice is to uninstall it or apply the fix manually.\n\nLet me write a remediation that is specific and actionable.<value>立即卸载 com_ionfiles 组件（如业务不需要）；若必须使用，手动修改 `components/com_ionfiles/download.php` 第 32 行，对 `$_GET['file']` 参数执行 `basename()` 和 `realpath()` 校验，禁止路径包含 `../` 或 `..\\\\` 字符，并将 `open_basedir` 限制在组件目录内。同时通过 `.htaccess` 限制对 `download.php` 的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/32377","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31877","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/46039","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6809","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6080.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-6080.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-6080.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0046a45cb220e45d345b72de014f969fbf07f97c/cves/2008/6xxx/CVE-2008-6080.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2008-6080-1380.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2008-6080-1383.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-6080_28.yaml","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/Vulnerability-Templates/template2/cve-2008-6080-1385.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Apr/09/Reports/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/rishikesh-j/Nuclei-Templates-Scrapped/blob/c1c4a009b3ada12b7923dcbc40e099ce8f224b2c/templates/cve-2008-6080-1380.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-6080-1384_1.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0011","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-5587","title":"phpPgAdmin 4.2.1 `_language` 参数目录遍历漏洞","description":"phpPgAdmin 4.2.1 及之前版本的 libraries/lib.inc.php 文件中存在目录遍历漏洞。当 PHP 环境的 register_globals 选项启用时，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 _language 参数传递包含 ../ 的恶意路径，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致数据库配置文件、系统凭证等敏感信息泄露。攻击无需认证，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2008-5587"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-12-16T19:07:31.843","updated":"2026-06-16T23:00:37.567","remediation":"升级 phpPgAdmin 至 4.2.1-1.1 及以上版本（Debian  unstable 对应 4.2.1-1.1，Debian Etch 对应 4.0.1-3.1etch1）。同时在 php.ini 中将 `register_globals` 设为 Off（PHP 5.3+ 已废弃该选项，PHP 5.4+ 已移除），并确保 `_language` 参数经过白名单校验，禁止包含 `../` 等路径遍历字符。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器层面（如 Apache mod_rewrite）拦截包含 `_language=../` 的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-security-announce/2009-02/msg00002.html","http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-updates/2012-04/msg00033.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/33014","http://secunia.com/advisories/33263","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/4737","http://www.debian.org/security/2008/dsa-1693","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/32670","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/47140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/7363","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-5587.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-5587.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-5587.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2008-5587-1378.yaml","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2008/README.md","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2008-5587-1376.yaml","https://github.com/nottrobin/ubuntu-cve-tracker/blob/36e411296b5707284049ec2e0db8d2622feca498/retired/CVE-2008-5587","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/fedora_2008-11564.nasl","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-debian/blob/b504c563e52b82e368fb82bf2033317b7c351e61/tracker/CVE/2008/CVE-2008-5587.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2008-5587-1377.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Jan/15/Reports/Report.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0010","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-5281","title":"South River Technologies Titan FTP Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"South River Technologies Titan FTP Server 6.05 存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 DELE 命令触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Titan FTP Server 6.05 build 550 及之前版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2008-5281"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-11-29","updated":"2008-11-29","remediation":"立即升级 Titan FTP Server 至最新版本（该漏洞已在 6.05 build 550 之后的版本修复）；由于旧版 Titan FTP Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Titan MFT 或 Titan SFTP Server。如无法升级，在防火墙层面限制 FTP 端口（默认 21）的可信源 IP 白名单，并在服务器上禁用 DELE 命令或限制其执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/31105","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-5281.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-5281.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-5281.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/5xxx/CVE-2008-5281.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-5281_9.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0287dd3c7f7460ce5db63d69ee5530c51a548735/CVE/data/2008/CVE-2008-5281.json","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-5281.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2008/CVE-2008-5281.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/179c45b9fa0538b72b0d380b72ed3445aca781eb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gfhc-mhqj-6287/GHSA-gfhc-mhqj-6287.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/2008/CVE-2008-5281.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-5281_28.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0009","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-4764","title":"Joomla! eXtplorer 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 eXtplorer 组件（com_extplorer）2.0.0 RC2 及更早版本中存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 show_error 动作中的 dir 参数传递包含 ..（点点）的恶意路径，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用复杂度低，影响大量使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2008-4764"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-10-28T02:03:38.003","updated":"2026-06-16T22:58:29.707","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 com_extplorer 组件，该扩展已停止维护不再有安全更新。若必须使用，升级至已修复目录遍历漏洞的最新版本；在 .htaccess 中添加 `RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} (\\.\\./|%2e%2e%2f)` 过滤 `dir` 参数中的 `../` 序列；配置 Web 服务器禁止组件目录的对外访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/28764","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/41873","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/5435","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-4764.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-4764.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-4764.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/4xxx/CVE-2008-4764.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2008-4764-1373.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2008-4764-1372.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-4764_28.yaml","https://github.com/0xelixer/Custom-tools/blob/5a8a731d0d786ba39fea598b3f40f8a8e845d482/priv/CVE-2008-4764.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Feb/09/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/foreztgump/cve_json/blob/b5f345eafeb97dce3fe03de3869b187e0574a5c0/2008/CVE-2008-4764.json","https://github.com/merlinepedra/nuclei-templates-1/blob/e218b90ed2c21978e92668478a9f1cc47b268f72/cves/2008/CVE-2008-4764.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0008","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-4668","title":"Joomla! Image Browser 目录遍历漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Joomla! 的 Image Browser（com_imagebrowser）组件 0.1.5 rc2 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 index.php 的 folder 参数中插入 `../` 路径遍历序列，实现包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞影响运行 Joomla! 并安装该组件的系统，CVSS 评分 9.0，危害等级高，攻击者可利用此漏洞读取敏感信息或在特定条件下执行任意代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9,"aliases":["CVE-2008-4668"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-10-22T10:30:01.240","updated":"2026-06-16T22:58:16.643","remediation":"立即在 Joomla! 后台卸载并删除 com_imagebrowser 0.1.5 rc2 组件（该组件已停止维护，官方未发布安全补丁）。若必须保留，在网站根目录 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} folder=\\.\\.(/) [NC] 并 RewriteRule 返回 403 阻断目录遍历攻击；同时在 PHP 层对 $_GET['folder'] 做白名单校验，拒绝包含 .. 或 / 开头的路径输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://securityreason.com/securityalert/4464","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31458","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/45490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/6618","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-4668.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-4668.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-4668.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/4xxx/CVE-2008-4668.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2008-4668-1367.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2008-4668.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-4668_46.yaml","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x32000/31458/info.html","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2008-4668_2.yaml","https://github.com/elijah-bennett0/IntentLimit/blob/bcfe225cf61ee454aa53896f7f3120246f52119f/tools/exploitation/CrazyIngrate/exploits/cve_2008_4668/cve_2008_4668.py","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Mar/26/Reports/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0004","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-1547","title":"Microsoft Outlook Web Access for Exchange Server 2003 开放重定向漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Web Access（OWA）for Exchange Server 2003 SP2 的 exchweb/bin/redir.asp 页面存在开放重定向漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 URL 参数传入恶意构造的链接，诱使用户点击后跳转到任意外部网站，进而实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响 Exchange Server 2003 SP2（build 6.5.7638），CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。此类重定向漏洞可被用于窃取用户凭据或传播恶意软件，建议用户升级至受支持版本或安装相应安全更新。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2008-1547"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-10-21T01:18:01.927","updated":"2026-06-16T22:51:57.103","remediation":"建议立即将 Exchange Server 2003 SP2 升级到受支持的 Exchange Server 2016/2019 或迁移至 Exchange Online，以彻底消除此漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 IIS 中对 exchweb/bin/redir.asp 添加 URL 重写规则，过滤并阻断非白名单域名的 URL 参数传递，或直接禁用 redir.asp 页面（通过 IIS 删除该文件处理映射）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://securityreason.com/securityalert/4441","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497374/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497390/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497433/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497500/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/497534/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/31765","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/46061","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/32489","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1547.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-1547.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/bba0a48d3746c10d09d381193c6f11ed1cfdb9ad/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1547.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/1xxx/CVE-2008-1547.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-1547_6_1.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-1547_4.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/5137a2fdc09885ac43f2e168868a96a399db1177/2008/CVE-2008-1547.json","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2008/CVE-2008-1547.rules","https://github.com/Yuy0ung/devsecops-platform/blob/cfbe213dd3cba9e1005e92ba7822bfd30e65f5c0/engines/dast-engine/poc/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1547.yaml","https://github.com/abh2technology/abh2-custom-templates-nucleiengine/blob/c7ba146f8016161974a9cf9f812ae7f225d23065/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1547.yaml","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/f2d12f176efdb99f18928b2678d34b7fa4f530f8/content/CVE-2008-1547.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0007","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-2650","title":"CMSimple 3.1 本地文件包含与任意文件上传漏洞","description":"CMSimple 3.1 存在目录遍历漏洞，当 PHP 的 register_globals 选项开启时，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 sl 参数传递 `../` 路径序列实现任意本地文件包含与执行。攻击者可先包含 adm.php 文件，再通过上传功能进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 CMSimple 3.1 版本，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中危。厂商已于 2008 年 6 月发布修补版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2008-2650"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-06-10T18:32:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:54:10.330","remediation":"CMSimple 已针对 3.1 版本发布了安全补丁，应立即升级至修补后的 3.1 版本（版本号未变但已修复）。同时强制关闭 PHP `register_globals` 选项（在 php.ini 中设置 `register_globals = Off`），并对用户输入 `sl` 参数进行严格的路径过滤，禁止包含 `../` 等路径遍历字符。如该 CMS 已停止维护，建议迁移至其他仍在安全更新的内容管理系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/45881","http://secunia.com/advisories/30463","http://www.cmsimple.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=17","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/29450","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/42792","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/42793","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/5700","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-2650.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-2650.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-2650.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2008-2650-1363.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/2xxx/CVE-2008-2650.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2008-2650-1358.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-2650_1.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-2650_6.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2008-2650-1360.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2008-2650.js","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/Vulnerability-Templates/template2/cve-2008-2650-1361.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0006","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-2398","title":"AppServ Open Project 2.5.10 跨站脚本漏洞（XSS）","description":"AppServ Open Project 2.5.10 及更早版本的 index.php 中存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者可向 appservlang 参数注入恶意 Web 脚本或 HTML 代码，在用户浏览器中执行任意脚本，窃取会话凭证或实施钓鱼攻击。攻击无需认证，仅需诱使用户访问特制链接即可触发，影响使用 AppServ 搭建的 Web 应用环境。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2008-2398"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2008-05-21T13:24:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:53:42.353","remediation":"AppServ 官方已停止维护该项目，建议用户迁移至其他活跃维护的 Web 服务器集成环境（如 XAMPP、WampServer）。如仍需继续使用，应在 index.php 中对 appservlang 参数进行严格的 HTML 编码过滤，使用 htmlspecialchars() 函数处理用户输入；同时在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面添加规则拦截包含 <script>、onerror、onload 等 XSS 特征的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/30333","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/3896","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/492271/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/29291","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/42546","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/31808","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2008-2398"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2008/AVE-2008-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0005","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-2052","title":"Bitrix Site Manager 开放重定向漏洞","description":"Bitrix Site Manager 6.5 的 redirect.php 中存在开放重定向漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 goto 参数传入恶意 URL，诱骗用户访问钓鱼网站或恶意站点。该漏洞属于 CWE-601 类型，无需身份认证即可利用，攻击者可通过社会工程手段诱导用户点击特制链接实现跳转劫持。CVSS 评分 6.1，危害等级中危，影响使用 Bitrix Site Manager 6.5 的所有 Web 应用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.1,"aliases":["CVE-2008-2052"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-05-02T17:05:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:53:00.587","remediation":"升级至 Bitrix Site Manager 6.5.2 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，修改 redirect.php 对 goto 参数做白名单校验，仅允许跳转到本站域名或预定义的合法外部 URL，拒绝除 http(s) 外的协议并过滤空协议链接；同时可在 web 服务器层（如 Apache mod_rewrite 或 Nginx）限制 redirect.php 仅接收本站 Referer 来源的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-0